issue.title: Runtime exception when syncing
issue.body:
## Operating System
Windows 11

## Runtime Version
.NET 8.0.1

## Error Message
Unhandled exception: System.InvalidOperationException: Sequence contains no elements

## Stack Trace
System.InvalidOperationException: Sequence contains no elements
   at SupportConcierge.Sync.Worker.Run()

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Run `dotnet run`
2. Open the dashboard
3. Click Sync

## Expected Behavior
Sync completes successfully

## Actual Behavior
App crashes with an exception
